lead_paragraph: As Minnesota Timberwolves forward Nemanja Bjelica let a 3-pointer fly at the buzzer, Denver Nuggets coach Michael Malone was already preparing for overtime.

headline.print_headline: Nuggets Hold On for 102-99 Win Over Timberwolves
